channel.title: Paroxyzm - 'sea dweller' (ft. ИeXus, The Osprey & LittleSpikes)
channel.description:
![sea%20dweller|500x500](upload://4azFkOYO3iv09IXZbRQ6ykBBpmz.jpeg)
You may have seen the post about this collab a while ago when it was only an idea, but now it's a reality. Big thanks to @tictacto, @The_Osprey and @LittleSpikes for contributing to this track!
**sea dweller** - https://soundcloud.com/paroxyzm-music/sea-dweller
We decided to split up this track into sections (one for each producer). If you want to see when each section starts and ends, the information is in the description on the track.
***Everyone involved:*** My Soundcloud - https://soundcloud.com/paroxyzm-music NeXus (inactive) - https://soundcloud.com/xenocutter The Osprey - https://soundcloud.com/devyn-fidel LittleSpikes - https://soundcloud.com/littlespikes
